### Create apk

npm run prebuild

cd android
./gradlew assembleRelease

### Bundle

./gradlew bundleRelease --no-daemon

### Emulator

emulator -list-avds
emulator -avd DEVICE_NAME

cd android/app/build/outputs/apk/release/
adb install app-release.apk

### Remote deploy

Android
Setting/developer/wireless debugging
enable
Pair with code

adb pair 192.168.0.187:<pairing_port>
enter code

adb connect 192.168.0.187:<connecting_port>

adb devices

adb -s <serial> install app.apk

adb disconnect 192.168.0.187:<connecting_port>
